post_content: I am newly returning to this site but I am a long time collector of Jake Stahl and used to be a member here a decade ago when I was a kid. I have been slowly adding to this collection for nearly two decades and am looking to add some new things or bring in more of the same. If anyone has anything Stahl related they are looking to sell or trade I am always interested for the right deal. Let me know what you got and thank you.
Also, if anyone knows where I can find a list of all the known Stahl T206 and T205 variations I would appreciate it.

If you click on the back info it will give you a list of all the confirmed T206 backs for each of the two Stahl poses.

[url]https://www.t206resource.com/Checklist.html?appSession=1XCA0L148WK2162123417783T93PYK8FNB55R3899V335V08OIL4QD0X4D6WPH8GL3A599F7A8L9T90YTJ7YO3ZG5GSV3AVYJK833N8CMOR303062OBFRNZK1T89TWD0[/url]
Appreciate it! I have been looking for this for years now.
I have an SGC 4 stahl glove shows AB350 if that helps. Shoot me a PM if you like. Good luck.
